CONTEXT Try5 IN ENGLISH
  CLASSIFY B ISA BorEorA
  CLASSIFY E ISA BorEorA
  CLASSIFY A ISA BorEorA

PATTERN Try5
RELATION r[X*Y]
RELATION s[X*A]
RELATION t[B*Y]
RELATION u[E*Y]
RULE Try5: r = s;(t/\u)
ENDPATTERN

ENDCONTEXT

{-
   Purpose: This is an attempt to mislead the type checker, by
            choosing a different source and target for t and u.
   Result:
try5a.adl:11:20 error:
  Cannot match the source concepts on the left side of the intersection.
     The source of t is B
     The source of u is E
  
  Type analysis:
  [B*Y] t[B*Y]/\u[E*Y]
  [B*Y]     ├── t[B*Y]
  [E*Y]     └── u[E*Y]

-}